_exptl_crystal_magnetic_properties_details
;
NPD
Non-standard parent setting: P2_1/n
The refined Co/Mn occupancies in the sample give a degree of order of 94% at the B-sublattice.
Structural and magnetic refinements performed at 2K
The moments of the Mn and Co sites have been constrained to be equal in the refinement
FM ordering of Co2+/Mn4+ moments below ca. 70 K
Magnetic order of Er moments develops below 30 K (AFM coupling between Er and Co/Mn sublattices). Incomplete order of Er moments at 2 K.
;

_active_magnetic_irreps_details
;
1k magnetic structure
k-maximal magnetic symmetry
1-dim active irrep: equivalent to the MSG assignment
Ferrimagnetic ground state
Non-polar symmetry. Type II multiferroicity is not possible, in contradiction with some previous publications.
;

